# Claude Bridge Native CLI - Brain Directory

This directory contains the persistent memory, identity, and knowledge systems
that make the bot an intelligent agentic coder.

## Directory Structure

```
brain/
├── identity/          # Identity, personality, preferences
├── memory/            # Conversation history, embeddings, knowledge
├── projects/          # Per-project context and decisions
├── tasks/             # Task queue and history
├── heartbeats/        # Activity logs and metrics
└── logs/              # Error logs and audit trails
```

## Initialization

The brain is automatically initialized on first run.
